1198
01:03:50,400 --> 01:03:53,040
Cos we are against the clock,
bear that in mind, OK?

1199
01:03:53,080 --> 01:03:54,960
And durability,
at the same time.

1200
01:03:55,000 --> 01:03:57,000
So you've gotta get
up this road,

1201
01:03:57,040 --> 01:03:58,840
which goes all
the way up there,

1202
01:03:58,880 --> 01:04:00,440
as fast as possible,

